Cross-Engine Dependencies
DRE integrates with but does not own:
SIG — raw signal feeds
PIE — downstream insight extraction
GGP — governance over actionability
CDE — research publication (if externalized)

Completion Criteria
DRE documentation is complete when:
NS-DRE-000 → NS-DRE-014 exist
Research artifacts are reproducible and explainable
Long-horizon insights do not leak into execution without governance